### Todo API 测试文件
### 使用 VS Code "REST Client" 扩展运行
### 安装: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### ==================== 待办事项接口 ====================

### 1. 获取待办列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos?page=1&pageSize=10

### 2. 创建待办
POST {{baseUrl}}/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试任务 - 优先级高",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "tags": ["测试", "重要"]
}

### 3. 获取所有标签
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos?action=tags

### 4. 按标签筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos?action=byTag&tag=测试

### 5. 搜索待办
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos?search=测试

### ==================== 单个待办操作 (需要替换 {id}) ====================

### 6. 更新待办 (先从上面的响应中复制 id)
# PATCH {{baseUrl}}/todos/{todo-id}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "name": "更新后的测试任务",
#   "completed": false,
#   "priority": "medium",
#   "tags": ["测试", "已更新"]
# }

### 7. 删除待办
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/todos/{todo-id}

### ==================== 子任务接口 ====================

### 8. 获取子任务
# GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/{todo-id}/subtasks

### 9. 获取子任务进度
# GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/{todo-id}/subtasks?action=progress

### 10. 创建子任务
# POST {{baseUrl}}/todos/{todo-id}/subtasks
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "name": "子任务 1"
# }

### 11. 更新子任务
# PATCH {{baseUrl}}/subtasks/{subtask-id}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "name": "更新后的子任务",
#   "completed": true
# }

### 12. 删除子任务
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/subtasks/{subtask-id}

### ==================== 附件接口 ====================

### 13. 获取附件列表
# GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/{todo-id}/attachments

### 14. 上传附件 (需要使用 form-data，建议用 Postman 或前端测试)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/todos/{todo-id}/attachments
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data
#
# file: @/path/to/file.pdf

### 15. 删除附件
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/attachments/{attachment-id}
